2024-09-28 17:12:42 - StudioAtrium\Entity\Discuss\Post:Insert {"timestamp":1727543562,"user_id":null,"user_ip":"83.31.94.155","user_browser":"Mozilla\/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64; rv:130.0) Gecko\/20100101 Firefox\/130.0","dao_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post\\DAO\\PDOMySQL","dao_event":"dao_object_insert","entity_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post","entity_data":{"id":10183,"__foreign_props":[],"parent_id":"0","cat_id":"100","project_id":"1632","nick":"Tomasz Zakrzewski","topic":"Tango V","content":"Witam,\r\n\r\nJestem wst\u0119pnie zainteresowany ofert\u0105:\r\n\r\nProjekt domu\r\nTango V\r\n\r\nMam pytanie jaka jest grubo\u015b\u0107 ocieplenia we\u0142n\u0105 w cm?\r\nDrugie czy istnieje mo\u017cliwo\u015b\u0107 projektu bez dodatkowych elewacji b\u0119d\u0105cych poza obr\u0119bem samego domu ?\r\nTrzecie czy jest mo\u017cliwo\u015b\u0107 dowozu oraz monta\u017cu?\r\nJe\u017celi tak to jaka by\u0142a by to kwota w przypadku adresu:\r\nSulej\u00f3wek\r\nul. D\u0142uga 6\r\n05-071?\r\n\r\nPozdrawiam,\r\nTomasz Zakrzewski","create_date":"2024-09-28 17:12:42","modify_date":"2024-09-28 17:12:42","status":"published","is_moderated":0,"attachments":[],"_uid":2606895},"entity_changes":false}
